      "description": "Hey there! If you're looking for a ride that truly feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor, you\u2019ve found it! This beauty is in absolute pristine condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since day one and it shows. Not a scratch or a dent in sight, and the interior is just as spotless. It drives like an absolute dream and is ready for its next big adventure. Honestly, it\u2019s rare to find one kept this well. Come take a look and see for yourself!",
