      "description": "Offering an immaculate 2011 Porsche 911 Carrera S (997.2), a definitive driver\u2019s specification featuring the 3.8L Direct Fuel Injection (DFI) flat-six and a 6-speed manual gearbox. This example exhibits flawless mechanical provenance, supported by a clean DME report and comprehensive service records. The chassis remains taut, utilizing Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) to deliver surgical handling, while the braking system retains its factory-spec bite with zero glazing on the rotors. Every component, from the limited-slip differential to the cooling system, operates within original factory tolerances. This is a museum-quality specimen with zero fluid migration and a pristine undercarriage, representing the ultimate analog experience in modern packaging.",
